  <subsection xml:id="subsection-week3-concepts">
    <title>Conceptual Review Questions</title>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          What are the ways that an implicit derivative can be
          undefined?
        </li>
        <li>
          What is a singularity?
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
